#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:1 of
msgid "Compute the 2-dimensional inverse discrete Fourier Transform."
msgstr "计算二维离散傅里叶逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:3 of
msgid ""
"This function computes the inverse of the 2-dimensional discrete Fourier "
"Transform over any number of axes in an M-dimensional array by means of "
"the Fast Fourier Transform (FFT).  In other words, ``ifft2(fft2(a)) == "
"a`` to within numerical accuracy.  By default, the inverse transform is "
"computed over the last two axes of the input array."
msgstr ""
"此函数通过快速傅里叶变换（FFT）计算 M 维数组中任意数量轴上的二维离散"
"傅里叶变换的逆变换。换句话说，在数值精度范围内，``ifft2(fft2(a)) == a``。"
"默认情况下，逆变换是在输入数组的最后两个轴上计算的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:9 of
msgid ""
"The input, analogously to `ifft`, should be ordered in the same way as is"
" returned by `fft2`, i.e. it should have the term for zero frequency in "
"the low-order corner of the two axes, the positive frequency terms in the"
" first half of these axes, the term for the Nyquist frequency in the "
"middle of the axes and the negative frequency terms in the second half of"
" both axes, in order of decreasingly negative frequency."
msgstr ""
"与 `ifft` 类似，输入应按照 `fft2` 返回的顺序排列，即两个轴的低阶角应包含"
"零频率项，这些轴的前半部分包含正频率项，轴的中间包含奈奎斯特频率项，两个"
"轴的后半部分按负频率递减排列负频率项。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2 of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:16 of
msgid "Input tensor, can be complex."
msgstr "输入张量，可以是复数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:18 of
msgid ""
"Shape (length of each axis) of the output (``s[0]`` refers to axis 0, "
"``s[1]`` to axis 1, etc.).  This corresponds to `n` for ``ifft(x, n)``. "
"Along each axis, if the given shape is smaller than that of the input, "
"the input is cropped.  If it is larger, the input is padded with zeros. "
"if `s` is not given, the shape of the input along the axes specified by "
"`axes` is used.  See notes for issue on `ifft` zero padding."
msgstr ""
"输出的形状（每个轴的长度）（``s[0]`` 表示轴 0，``s[1]`` 表示轴 1，等等）"
"。这对应于 ``ifft(x, n)`` 中的 `n`。在每个轴上，如果给定的形状小于输入的"
"形状，则输入会被裁剪。如果大于输入，则输入会被零填充。如果未给出 `s`，则"
"使用输入在由 `axes` 指定的轴上的形状。有关 `ifft` 零填充问题，请参见说明"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:25 of
msgid ""
"Axes over which to compute the FFT.  If not given, the last two axes are "
"used.  A repeated index in `axes` means the transform over that axis is "
"performed multiple times.  A one-element sequence means that a one-"
"dimensional FFT is performed."
msgstr ""
"用于计算 FFT 的轴。如果未给出，则使用最后两个轴。`axes` 中的重复索引表示"
"对该轴多次进行变换。单元素序列表示执行一维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:30 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `mt.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `mt.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2 of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:33 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axes"
" indicated by `axes`, or the last two axes if `axes` is not given."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 被截断或零填充的输入，沿 `axes` 指示的轴进行变换，如果未给出 `"
"axes`，则沿最后两个轴进行变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2 of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2 of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:37 of
msgid ""
"If `s` and `axes` have different length, or `axes` not given and     "
"``len(s) != 2``."
msgstr "如果 `s` 和 `axes` 的长度不同，或者未给出 `axes` 且 ``len(s) != 2``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:38 of
msgid "If an element of `axes` is larger than than the number of axes of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axes` 的某个元素大于 `a` 的轴数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:42 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:43 of
msgid ""
"Overall view of discrete Fourier transforms, with definitions and "
"conventions used."
msgstr "离散傅里叶变换的总体视图，包含所用的定义和约定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:45 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:46 of
msgid "The forward 2-dimensional FFT, of which `ifft2` is the inverse."
msgstr "二维正向 FFT，`ifft2` 是其逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:48 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:49 of
msgid "The inverse of the *n*-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "*n* 维 FFT 的逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:51 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:52 of
msgid "The one-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "一维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:54 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:55 of
msgid "The one-dimensional inverse FFT."
msgstr "一维逆 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:58 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:59 of
msgid "`ifft2` is just `ifftn` with a different default for `axes`."
msgstr "`ifft2` 只是 `ifftn`，但 `axes` 的默认值不同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:61 of
msgid ""
"See `ifftn` for details and a plotting example, and `numpy.fft` for "
"definition and conventions used."
msgstr ""
"有关详细信息和绘图示例，请参见 `ifftn`，有关定义和所用约定，请参见 `numpy"
".fft`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifft2.ifft2:64 of
msgid ""
"Zero-padding, analogously with `ifft`, is performed by appending zeros to"
" the input along the specified dimension.  Although this is the common "
"approach, it might lead to surprising results.  If another form of zero "
"padding is desired, it must be performed before `ifft2` is called."
msgstr ""
"与 `ifft` 类似，零填充是通过在指定维度上向输入追加零来实现的。尽管这是"
"常见做法，但可能导致意外结果。如果需要其他形式的零填充，则必须在调用 `"
"ifft2` 之前完成。"

